column5: But like, where is the evidence that the above statement is true, give me an example. As to the family I feel you, one of the reasons I'm here.
Yes. We were materially privileged and emotionally starved. Why the loss of my home hit me so hard, come to think of it. Shit.
Yes but if I dont take them I'm so depressed I'll die by my own hand.
My sister did.
Why do you feel if you died it would be good? I'm not mocking I'm honestly neutral and want to help if I can.

I'm so sorry for the cards you were dealt. I have ptsd and things I really care about were stolen from me and I cant ever get them (and my life) back unless I win the lottery. So I feel this statement.
I even fantasized about suicide by cop. Sad. Hopefully I won't do it.

We have a saying in trauma circles. (For the record I also get told this a lot, the strong thing.) 
"I didnt need to be strong; I  needed to be safe."
Hello!
There is something poisonous about the rapist, not about you.
This made me weep. Please dont go that way.
I want you to fix my broken life which unless you're a billionaire you can't. I want to be saved from this fate. I want to go back in time. I want to undo this rape of my soul.

Great post man. Ironically I'm here cause something very important to me was taken away and I was unable to grieve and move on. Life went from sad to agony. I really hear you. Worst part is the people spouting this cliche shit think they are helping when really they have no idea how fucking lucky they are.
None is my understanding from the research I've done. But the people who write them arent in our shoes and dont realize their idea of help is very inadequate.
I'm sorry if I invalidated you or made you feel worse it was not my intention.
My bf gets this sometimes in his case it was perfomance anxiety and antidepressants doc gave him Viagra he was fine. Itll be ok.
Yes.
I know it hurts. I don't want you to die.

Hi there. My story is a bit different but the same pattern, complex trauma, shitty childhood, something devastating in adulthood that just...shatters what was left of who you are. I second the comment below of trauma therapy. Have you tried any of these: EMDR, Somatic Experiencing,  Sensory Motor, TFT, CPT? I know its fucking demoralizing I'm still trying not to die myself. Please hang on.
I want you to know I read this and I'm listening.
Age 32.

32. Severe complex trauma from a very bad childhood. Was re-traumatized when my home was taken away, the safe place that kept me emotionally stable, gone. My hibernating cptsd bear woke up and man, was he pissed. I got very Ill. Lost 45 pounds, couldnt eat, slept 14 hours. Still suicidal. 2019 took everything that made me safe and happy and gave it to someone else. I dont go into detail on here about it much cause I've gotten some pretty unhelpful replies.
I am so glad. We are always here too.

You have no self-esteem and it sounds like you have childhood trauma like me. A trauma/relational therapist and one who specializes in helping trans people could help you. I know it's hard but they can really help.
Me too, and I'm addicted to chocolate and porn. I feel pathetic.
Sorry but no. You dont know why someone is suicidal. That's a very dangerous assumption friend.

Holy shit. This is the worst thing I've ever read on here. I am so sorry but that doesn't even cover it. Please get everyone to a trauma specialist asap for processing  to minimize the damage. God how awful.
I'm sorry your family is so invalidating. Do you have PTSD from the wreck? Try EMDR.
No. Pain is subjective. I say that as a person with complex ptsd who has lost everything I cared about.
Hi there

And here we are living and want to die. 

Respect.

I am so sorry. I'll leave this here for you if you like. National Sexual Abuse Hotline:

Call 1-800-656-4673
Available 24 hours everyday
A fucking men.
Is there a local women's dv line near you? This is exactly what they do. Please call them. You dont deserve abuse.
I'm here if you like I'm going thru this now much respect.
Yea fuck this virus and everything that came with it. Fuck 2019.
I hate it cause it's so damned unfair. So cruel. Gives you things just to wrench them away.

I'm glad things turned around for you. I have ptsd and all the meds and therapy and shocks arent working. People won't donate to my GoFundMe so they'd never do what your friends did. Dude I envy you. Good for you!
It certainly feels like we cant have nice things.
Do you have a trauma history? It would explain all this. If you can find an EMDR specialist they can help.
Yikes so sorry.
Yea, lack of money and power landed me on this sub. Respect to you man.
I have these thoughts too. I want people to suffer for what they did to me.
Did it stop the pain? I'm so sorry.
Yea I feel this hardcore. You have my sympathy and ear.
I'm here. What's your fave place to visit?
It's such a terrible feeling, I feel doomed too. I wished I could save us all.
Same, lol.
Dude I am so there right now in this shit. Solidarity brother.
I think about this too, revenge suicide. Make sure everyone knows who fucking did this to me.
I'm so sorry. One event took all my happiness too. Have you tried p.t. for the pain it saved my life.
I won't insult you by saying I've been there but as A chick I'd rather sleep with a 4 inch guy than a 9 inch guy.
It's such a horrible feeling.
Me but this shit isnt remotely unpleasant it's agony.
I wonder if it would be better ir if the Karma folks are right and I'd just suffer all over again.
My ptsd is just so bad...acute on top of chronic. I'm also dealing with professional incompetence in my area.
Me too.
This spoke to me man it's where I'm at it fucking sucks hard cock.
Maybe I should but no. There is even a virus support line in my area I called it. The government got us into this mess by not closing the border sooner.
I'll talk.

If there is one thing I truly believe, and after MDD I dont believe in much anymore, it is that the people on this sub do not deserve this, you included. Fuck man even me. Read Lost Connections by Johann he talks about this so well.
Please dont go away. Talk to us instead. What got you here friend?
I did move out but a year later I'm still struggling and stuck. I just wished the guy who..changed my life for the worse had never come into it. I'd be happy now.
I dont, if you mean killing myself. I just, I'm tired of life being nothing but pain. If you mean the life insurance so my mom will be taken care of. I haven't finalized this it was just a dark idea.
Try a low cost clinic or even a hospital or State Health Dept explain it's an emergency and you are suicidal from pain.
Sometimes I think staying alive is the real hell.
I would, but I feel people screwed me over and I'd want it to be very clear why I was dead and who really killed me.
Oh man that sucks I am so sorry.
Hey man the 1st time I was suicidal it was over physical pain. It's a terrible place to be. Talk to me. Can you sue the doc to at least get yourself some justice?
A pelvic P.T. can help you with that issue, saved my life.
I know this feeling.
I've reached the limit of what I can cope with and I'm just trying not to die.
I just wanna let you know I read this.
Sue the evil bitch. I am so sorry I know how soul-crushing trauma is.
I know what you mean about money solving shit I'm in the same sitch and I feel like nobody gets it till they r there. I was also from a bad home I'm here for you.
I wished it helped more. Ty friend. I just wanted everyone here to know they help me at my lowest.
Complex trauma, and having the thing I used to cope with it stolen away.
I am so sorry. I have trauma too. I'm here if you need me.
Yea, especially since my sibling just told me on the phone, "You die, I die."
Very nice.
Or a free thinker.
I feel like God wants me dead sometimes.
I love that. "GO SEE A THERAPIST." Yea dude I got 3.
I'm suicidal cause I was ousted from someplace I loved. I understand. It's all too real.
Yea. Me too man.
In my case I think it's pity.
I have a slowish thyroid probably from child abuse <its a thing look it up> I know it sux having weight issues and this Society hates us so much. I'm here if u wanna talk.
Yes...unless I win the lotto my problem is permanent. So feel this.
Please find a pelvic health aka women's health physical therapist they can help you with this!!! It is fixable. I'm not spouting bs either they saved my life.
You seem genuinely remorseful so I dont think you deserve to die. I usually say therapy is cliche but in a case like this I think a specialist or program could help you.
Agony. My life fell apart in May 2019. I would have missed the agony. The worst part is that it is true.
I have ptsd I care I hope you are ok.
Yeah. To 2017. Yes. God yes.
Probably electrocution which is nasty as all hell. I hate what my problems have turned me into.
Oblivion

You have a beautiful voice. I know the tone in it, and what you said about the pain not being worth it. I cant lecture you about that cause I'm fighting that beast myself I just wanted to say you seem like a cool person and please dont go away.

I lost everything that was important to me. Actually it was stolen away and there wasn't a damned thing I could do to stop it. The the angry bear that is CPTSD woke from his hibernation and mauled me. My life is in tatters. I found this place from a news article. No lectures about gratitude, starting over, etc please. Thanks.
You aren't pathetic to me. You write beautifully. Please tell us more. Please stay. I'm a writer too. I'm in so much pain too. I dont think you're a loser. I think you're an inspiration.
Yes..this hardcore. You understand me. I often feel like why even try? The deck was rigged from the start.
